column16: Brian Goodwin out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Tommy Pham.   Matt Wieters scores.
Mike Mayers intentionally walks Ryan Zimmerman.
Wilmer Difo out on a sacrifice fly to left fielder Randal Grichuk.   Adam Lind scores.  Matt Wieters advances to 3rd, on a throwing error by left fielder Randal Grichuk.
Matt Wieters doubles (13) on a sharp fly ball to center fielder Tommy Pham.   Adam Lind to 3rd.
Adam Lind singles on a sharp line drive to right fielder Stephen Piscotty.
Anthony Rendon grounds into a force out, shortstop Alex Mejia to second baseman Greg Garcia.   Daniel Murphy out at 2nd.
Bryce Harper flies out to left fielder Randal Grichuk.
Michael Taylor grounds out, third baseman Jedd Gyorko to first baseman Matt Carpenter.
Brian Goodwin grounds into a double play, second baseman Greg Garcia to shortstop Alex Mejia to first baseman Matt Carpenter.   Max Scherzer out at 2nd.
Wilmer Difo grounds out, first baseman Matt Carpenter to pitcher Mike Mayers.
Chris Iannetta strikes out on a foul tip.
Chris Herrmann flies out to right fielder Stephen Piscotty.   Chris Owings to 3rd.
Chris Owings doubles (21) on a line drive to left fielder Randal Grichuk.
Jake Lamb homers (18) on a fly ball to right center field.
Paul Goldschmidt grounds out, second baseman Greg Garcia to first baseman Matt Carpenter.
